title: About Preseason Update.
body: I am currently playing in NA.I want to ask that if I am level 30 before preseason wpuld I be getting those 30 chests.Please answer to my question.Username:TanmayKashyap Honar:5 Server:NA

replies.body: Great question!  Per the [Preseason FAQ](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/115012640908), those of us already 30 won't be receiving any chests or content.  We've already received IP for the games we played, which is what this new system will be replacing.
